comments: Hunter (ATL) reaches in and cleanly dislodges from DeRozan (CHI) as he starts his drive on the perimeter.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: The ball goes off of DeRozan's (CHI) foot last before it goes out of bounds.
Hunter (ATL) establishes himself in White's (CHI) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
While defending the drive, White (CHI) makes incidental foot-to-foot contact with Hunter (ATL) in the lane.
LaVine (CHI) legally contests Griffin's (ATL) jump shot attempt.
White (CHI) legally contests Young's (ATL) jump shot attempt.
DeRozan (CHI) legally contests Young's (ATL) jump shot attempt.
Capela (ATL) has an arm extended when he accepts the oncoming contact from with DeRozan (CHI). The contact is marginal while defending his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
LaVine (CHI) commits a take foul on Young (ATL).

Replay review of the foul called on White (CHI) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful and the call was overturned as White reaches in and cleanly dislodges the ball from Griffin (ATL).
Griffin (ATL) initiates contact with Jones Jr.'s (CHI) arm, which affects his play at the basket.
Jones Jr. (CHI) quickly places and releases his arm on Bogdanovic's (ATL) lower body as he enters his upward shooting motion.
Capela (ATL) gathers the pass on his right foot and takes two steps before he shoots the ball.
White (CHI) establishes himself in Young's (ATL) path and releases away, making slight contact with him while doing so.
White (CHI) legally contests Young's (ATL) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
White (CHI) legally contests Young's (ATL) jump shot attempt.
Bogdanovic (ATL) fails to get to the height of the ball and makes contact with DeRozan's (CHI) forearm on his shot attempt.
Jones Jr. (CHI) legally contests Griffin's (ATL) layup attempt.
